# MarketLive UI Checklist (Mandatory)

**Objective:** Maintain a high-density, operator-grade UI. NO FLUFF.

## 1. Typography & Density
- [ ] **Base Size:** All standard text MUST use `text-sm`.
- [ ] **Meta Data:** All labels, timestamps, and secondary info MUST use `text-xs`.
- [ ] **Headings:** Avoid oversized hero fonts. Max `text-2xl` for page titles.
- [ ] **Whitespace:** Tight spacing. Use `gap-2` or `gap-4` max for grids.

